.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

City: rome, edinburgh, paris, venice, marseilles
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
The people have 5 different jobs:  electrician, entrepreneur, chef, software-developer, journalist
The people have 5 different hobbies: romemaster, cooking, magic-tricks, sudoku, singing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: trance, d&b, indie, house, dubstep
1. the british is the person traveling to paris
2. the swedish is the fan of indie
3. the danish is the software-developer
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to venice
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is the entrepreneur
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of d&b
7. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's hobby is cooking
8. the chef is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the fan of trance
11. the fan of dubsteps is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking
12. the person who's hobby is romemaster is the electrician
13. the german is the person who's hobby is sudoku
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome
15. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the journalist

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| City		|    marseilles	|     rome	|      paris	|     edinburgh	|     venice	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| Music-Genre		|     trance	|    dubstep	|     d&b	|     house	|      indie	|
| Job	|    journalist	|     software-developer	|     chef	|    entrepreneur	|      electrician	|
| Hobby		|   cooking	|    singing	|  magic-tricks	|    sudoku	|   romemaster	|
